casebody.data:
Fourth Department,

January, 1953.

(January 7, 1953.) In the Matter of the Accounting of Manufacturers and Traders Trust Company, Successor to Lockport Exchange Trust Company, as Executor of Anderson Crowforth, Deceased, Appellant-Respondent. Masonic Temple Association of the City of Lockport, Respondent-Appellant; Annie Gummerson et al., Respondents.

Decree insofar as appealed from affirmed, with costs to all parties filing briefs payable out of the estate. All concur. (Appeals from part of a decree construing a will.) Present — Taylor, P. J., MeCurn, Kimball, Piper and Wheeler, JJ. [197 Misc. 781.]
